-- RBC Capital Markets Seeking U.K. Bank Acquisition, Financial Times Reports
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-06-14T00:19:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/rbc-capital-markets-seeking-u-k-bank-acquisition-financial-times-reports.html

          
          
             RBC Capital Markets is seeking to
buy a boutique investment bank in London and co-head  Doug McGregor  has held exploratory talks with possible targets, the
Financial Times reported, without saying how it obtained the
information.  
 Nick Fothergill will be appointed European head of equities
by RBC today, the newspaper also said.  
